<h1 id="changelog">Changelog</h1>

<p>All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file, in reverse chronological order by release.</p>

<h2 id="section">1.0.3</h2>

<p>Add <code>source</code> link in composer.json. No code changes.</p>

<h2 id="section-1">1.0.2</h2>

<p>Allow PSR-7 (psr/http-message) 2.0. No code changes.</p>

<h2 id="section-2">1.0.1</h2>

<p>Allow installation with PHP 8. No code changes.</p>

<h2 id="section-3">1.0.0</h2>

<p>First stable release. No changes since 0.3.0.</p>

<h2 id="section-4">0.3.0</h2>

<p>Added Interface suffix on exceptions</p>

<h2 id="section-5">0.2.0</h2>

<p>All exceptions are in <code>Psr\Http\Client</code> namespace</p>

<h2 id="section-6">0.1.0</h2>

<p>First release</p>
